folder: Franklin Avenue & Dean Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Franklin Avenue, at Dean Street. View 1 is south along the west side of Franklin Avenue, View 2 showing the corner end part of Dean Street. View 3 is north on Franklin Avenue from Dean, showing the west side.
P. L. Sperr
September 6, 1941
